# RTK

**Every Shell command starts with `rtk`.** No bare `git`, `cargo`, `pnpm`, `rg`, etc.

Hook (`rtk hook cursor`) rewrites misses — still write `rtk` yourself.

Meta: `rtk gain`, `rtk gain --history`, `rtk discover`, `rtk proxy <cmd>`

Full guide: `~/.agents/skills/rtk/SKILL.md`
